snippet.title: Outta Hand - Official Trailer | Upload VR Showcase 2023
snippet.description:
Check out the trailer for Outta Hand, the VR platformer where you walk on your hands to avoid all sorts of traps and falls, which is coming to Meta Quest later this year.

#SummerOfGaming #VR
